log.Sql: SELECT year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer , Sum(c20) AS c20, Sum(c40) AS c40, Sum(teu) AS Total, Sum(wtmt) AS wtmt FROM vw_tipo_container WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 09) AND fk_lporto In ('SANTOS','') AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_area In('FE','ISC','') AND fk_cliente In('GO TRANS GLOBAL LOGISTICA LTDA EPP','GO TRANS INTERNATIONAL LOGISTICS LTDA ME','') GROUP BY year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer

SELECT fk_lporto, fk_cliente, darea, fk_carrier, fk_odporto, fk_direction, year, Sum(c20) AS c20, Sum(c40) AS c40, Sum(teu)AS teu, Sum(wtmt) AS wtmt FROM vw_especifico_carrier_area WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 09) AND fk_lporto In ('SANTOS','') AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_area In('FE','ISC','') AND fk_cliente In('PANTOS','PANTOS LOGISTICS','PANTOS LOGISTICS CO LTD','')GROUP BY fk_lporto, fk_cliente, darea, fk_carrier, fk_odporto, fk_direction, year

SELECT year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer , Sum(c20) AS c20, Sum(c40) AS c40, Sum(teu) AS Total, Sum(wtmt) AS wtmt FROM vw_tipo_container WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 09) AND fk_lporto In ('SANTOS','') AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_area In('FE','ISC','') AND fk_cliente In('PANTOS','PANTOS LOGISTICS','PANTOS LOGISTICS CO LTD','') GROUP BY year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer

SELECT year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer , Sum(c20) AS c20, Sum(c40) AS c40, Sum(teu) AS Total, Sum(wtmt) AS wtmt FROM vw_tipo_container WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 09) AND fk_lporto In ('SANTOS','') AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_area In('FE','ISC','') AND fk_cliente In('ALFA CARGO','ALFA CARGO TRANSPORTES INTERNACIONAIS LTDA','') GROUP BY year, lcode, fk_lporto, cod, fk_direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_odporto, fk_tcontainer, dcontainer

SELECT year, fk_lporto, shcnee, fk_cliente, dregion, fk_odporto, fk_direction, Sum(teu) AS Total , code , (CASE WHEN code = 'EMC' THEN 1 WHEN code = 'ZIM' THEN 2 WHEN code = 'ALI' THEN 3 WHEN code = 'HJS' THEN 4 WHEN code = 'CGM' THEN 5 WHEN code = 'COSC' THEN 6 WHEN code = 'CSAV' THEN 7 WHEN code = 'HSUD' THEN 8 WHEN code = 'LIB' THEN 9 WHEN code = 'HPG' THEN 10 WHEN code = 'MOL' THEN 11 WHEN code = 'KLINE' THEN 12 WHEN code = 'MSC' THEN 13 WHEN code = 'MSK' THEN 14 WHEN code = 'NYK' THEN 15 WHEN code = 'PIL' THEN 16 WHEN code = 'SAF' THEN 17 WHEN code = 'HPG' THEN 18 WHEN code = 'CHS' THEN 19 WHEN code = 'OTHS' THEN 20 END) AS COD_NUM FROM vw_especifico_shipper_cnee WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 08) AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_cliente In('RIO MASTER IMPORTACAO E EXPORTACAO DE ARTIGOS PARA PRES','RIO MASTER IMPORTACAO E EXPORTACAO LTDA','') GROUP BY year, fk_lporto, shcnee, fk_cliente, dregion, fk_odporto, fk_direction , code , COD_NUM

SELECT owner, cliente, dporto , direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, fk_month, dmonth, year, currency , Sum(somadec20) AS c20, Sum(vlr20) AS vlr20, Sum(somadec40) AS c40, Sum(vlr40)AS vlr40, Sum(teus) AS teus, Sum(totalrev) AS totalrev FROM vw_summary_performance WHERE year = '2019' AND direction In('IMPORT','') AND fk_tcommodity In ('CF','') GROUP BY owner, cliente, dporto , direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, fk_month, dmonth, year, currency

SELECT owner, cliente, dporto , direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, fk_month, dmonth, year, currency , Sum(somadec20) AS c20, Sum(vlr20) AS vlr20, Sum(somadec40) AS c40, Sum(vlr40)AS vlr40, Sum(teus) AS teus, Sum(totalrev) AS totalrev FROM vw_summary_performance WHERE year = '2019' AND direction In('IMPORT','') AND fk_tcommodity In ('CF','') GROUP BY owner, cliente, dporto , direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, fk_month, dmonth, year, currency

SELECT year, fk_lporto, shcnee, fk_cliente, dregion, fk_odporto, fk_direction, Sum(teu) AS Total , code , (CASE WHEN code = 'EMC' THEN 1 WHEN code = 'ZIM' THEN 2 WHEN code = 'ALI' THEN 3 WHEN code = 'HJS' THEN 4 WHEN code = 'CGM' THEN 5 WHEN code = 'COSC' THEN 6 WHEN code = 'CSAV' THEN 7 WHEN code = 'HSUD' THEN 8 WHEN code = 'LIB' THEN 9 WHEN code = 'HPG' THEN 10 WHEN code = 'MOL' THEN 11 WHEN code = 'KLINE' THEN 12 WHEN code = 'MSC' THEN 13 WHEN code = 'MSK' THEN 14 WHEN code = 'NYK' THEN 15 WHEN code = 'PIL' THEN 16 WHEN code = 'SAF' THEN 17 WHEN code = 'HPG' THEN 18 WHEN code = 'CHS' THEN 19 WHEN code = 'OTHS' THEN 20 END) AS COD_NUM FROM vw_especifico_shipper_cnee WHERE year = '2019' AND(fk_month BETWEEN 01 AND 08) AND cod In('2','') AND fk_service In('ESA','') AND fk_cliente In('QUATTROR COMERCIAL LTDA','QUATTROR TRADING COMPANY LTDA','') GROUP BY year, fk_lporto, shcnee, fk_cliente, dregion, fk_odporto, fk_direction , code , COD_NUM

SELECT fk_month , dmonth , owner, cliente, fk_srep, direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, year, Sum(teus) AS Totalteus FROM vw_summary_cliente WHERE year = '2019' AND direction In('EXPORT','') GROUP BY fk_month , dmonth , owner, cliente, fk_srep, direction, fk_service, dservice, fk_bporto, year
